C         CNAME---CURRENT RELATION NAME SPECIFIED IN LOCREL
C         LRROW---LAST ROW SENT IN TUPLER
C         NRROW---NEXT AVAILABLE ROW FOR ADDING A TUPLE
C         RELMOD--MODIFICATION FLAG - O MEANS NO, 1 MEANS YES
